Class SubscriptionManager

java.lang.Object
  edu.uci.isr.yancees.server.core.AbstractPluginTreeBuilder
      edu.uci.isr.yancees.server.core.SubscriptionManager
public class SubscriptionManager
extends AbstractPluginTreeBuilder

This class is specialized in the SubscriptionManager. It provides a hierarchical implementation of the parser that allocates the plug-in in a bottom-up fashion, hooking them to their next father plug-in in the XML hierarchy.
